              <li>Developed workflow/AI management assistants, using React, Zustand, Tanstack, and more for core business modules (store, inventory, POS, etc.).</li>
              <li>Led frontend architecture and performance optimization for large-scale B2B SaaS, including PWA, SSR, and deep optimization for mobile and desktop.</li>
              <li>Built independent visualization tools and dashboards, using React and ECharts.</li>
              <li>Supported backend-for-frontend and microservices with Midway (NestJS-like) and API Gateway solutions.</li>
            </ul>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>weidian</strong> — Web Frontend Engineer<br />Apr 2021 – Jan 2022<br />
            <ul>
              <li>Responsible for business-side web development, including advertising, business modules, and admin panels.</li>
              <li>Mainly used Vue, JSX, Vuex, Vue-router.</li>
            </ul>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Zhejiang Dahua Technology</strong> — Web Frontend Engineer<br />May 2020 – Apr 2021<br />
            <ul>
              <li>Developed online training and exam platforms, using React, Redux, Webpack, and Node.js.</li>
            </ul>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Hangzhou Yuanshi Network Security</strong> — Intern<br />Jul 2018 – Sep 2018<br />
            <ul>
              <li>Participated in Android app development for logistics management, including UI, business logic, and API integration.</li>
            </ul>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>
      <section style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h2>Research Experience</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>High-dimensional Data Analysis</strong> — Graduation Thesis<br />Feb 2020 – Jun 2020<br />
            <ul>
              <li>Studied feature selection and classification for high-dimensional data, including SVM, gamma, and PCA.</li>
              <li>Used ResNet50 for image classification experiments.</li>
            </ul>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>
      <section style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h2>Others</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Maintainer of <a href="https://gitee.com/devui/devui" target="_blank">DevUI Vue3</a> open-source project, participated in technical sharing and project management.</li>
          <li>Participated in Huawei open-source community activities.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
